dct_description_sm: Zincographed at the Ordnance Survey Office, Southampton, 1885.
Compass rose oriented with north toward upper-right.
Legend of proposed boundaries shows "Parliamentary Divisions" and "Parliamentary Burghs."
Shows grassland, woods, waterways, city plans, small towns, geographical place names, reservoirs, named estates.
